lead_paragraph: Big Ten Commissioner Jim Delany does not envision the Rose Bowl abandoning its New Year's Day spot in order to accommodate the College Football Playoff semifinals.

headline.print_headline: Delany Does Not See Rose Bowl Move to Accommodate Playoffs
